parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The pitting failure of the camshaft can cause engine stalling, loss of power, and difficulty controlling the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
The sudden engine stalling or loss of power can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
